title: Ralph Cotton-Black Mesa
description:
Ralph Cotton-Black Mesa 
 A Ranger Sam Burrack Novel
	

Best-selling author and Pulitzer Prize nominee Ralph Cotton is hailed for his rough and tumble Westerns full of historical details. Although Ella Lang is now known as Queen of the Outlaws, there was a day when she and Ranger Sam Burrack were deeply in love. Now they're on opposite sides of the law and Burrack is out to rid the West of Lang's motley gang of outlaws.
